<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>About - InstaSnapper</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen animate-gradient bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-white">
  
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="flex items-center justify-between sm:justify-center px-4 sm:px-8 py-4 border-b border-black/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md shadow-md">
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
      <img src="../assets/images/logo.gif" alt="Logo" class="h-10 w-10 sm:h-12 sm:w-12" />
      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-[500] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#db00ff] to-[#22c8fe] text-transparent bg-clip-text">InstaSnapper</h1>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 text-left">
    <div class="text-white space-y-5 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Us</h2>

      <p>📸 <strong>Instasnapper</strong> is your go-to solution for downloading Instagram content instantly and hassle-free. Whether it’s a reel, post, or gallery, you can save it in just a few clicks. No logins, no confusion — just fast downloads. It’s built for users who value simplicity and speed. With Instasnapper, your favorite content is always a click away.</p>

      <p>🔗 Using Instasnapper is as easy as 1-2-3. Just copy the link of the Instagram post, paste it into the input box on our homepage, and click “Download.” The tool works seamlessly across mobile, desktop, and tablets, making content saving truly universal. No special extensions or software required. Everything runs directly in your browser.</p>

      <p>⚡ Fast. Reliable. Secure.</p>
      <p>🔒 No data is stored on our servers.</p>
      <p>💡 Just copy, paste, and save!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-gray-100 py-8 text-center text-gray-700">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center sm:space-x-8 space-y-2 sm:space-y-0 text-[18px] font-medium mb-4">
      <a href="/about" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition">About</a>
      <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition">Policy</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition">Contact</a>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-[500] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#db00ff] to-[#22c8fe] text-transparent bg-clip-text">
      InstaSnapper
    </h1>
  </footer>

  <!-- Animation -->
  <style>
    @keyframes gradient {
      0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }
    .animate-gradient {
      background-size: 200% 200%;
      animation: gradient 6s ease infinite;
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
